sequenceDiagram
    title 時序圖 — 操作員完整操控流程

    participant O as "操作員\nOperator"
    participant CP as "Web Cockpit\n(Next.js 3011)"
    participant API as "Backend API\n(Next.js 3010)"
    participant DB as "PostgreSQL\nDatabase"
    participant LK as "LiveKit SFU\n(v1.7.2)"
    participant EA as "Edge Agent\n(TypeScript)"
    participant GP as "Go Publisher\n(GStreamer)"
    participant R2 as "R2 Bridge\n(Python ROS2)"
    participant VH as "ROS2 Vehicle\n(Wheeltec AMR)"

    Note over O,VH: 階段 1 — 認證與車輛列表
    O->>CP: 輸入 Email / Password
    CP->>API: POST /api/v1/auth/login
    API->>DB: 查詢 User + 驗證密碼
    DB-->>API: 使用者資料
    API-->>CP: 回傳 Access Token + Refresh Cookie
    CP->>API: GET /api/v1/vehicles (Bearer Token)
    API->>DB: 查詢 VehiclePermission
    DB-->>API: 權限資料
    API-->>CP: 車輛列表 (含狀態)
    CP-->>O: 顯示車隊儀表板

    Note over O,VH: 階段 2 — 獲取控制租約
    O->>CP: 選擇車輛「AMR-01」
    CP->>API: POST /api/v1/vehicles/vehicle-001/control-lease/claim
    API->>DB: 建立 ControlLease (ACTIVE, 30min TTL)
    DB-->>API: Lease Created
    API-->>CP: Lease Claimed
    CP->>API: POST /api/v1/livekit/token
    API->>LK: 產生 Room Token (role: operator)
    LK-->>API: Token
    API-->>CP: LiveKit Token + Room 資訊

    Note over O,VH: 階段 3 — 連線 LiveKit 與串流
    CP->>LK: 加入 Room (WebRTC Subscribe Video + DataChannel)
    EA->>LK: 已存在 Room 中 (Edge Agent Participant)
    EA->>GP: IPC: start (LiveKit Token)
    activate GP
    GP->>GP: GStreamer NVENC H.264 編碼
    GP->>LK: 發佈 Video Track (ZED-X Front)
    LK-->>CP: 接收 Video Track → 渲染 <video>
    CP-->>O: 顯示雙路即時影像
    deactivate GP

    Note over O,VH: 階段 4 — 控制命令與 Telemetry
    O->>CP: 拖曳 Joystick (前進 0.5, 左轉 0.3)
    CP->>CP: encodeCommand(movement)
    CP->>LK: DataChannel Publish (ControlCommand)
    LK-->>EA: DataChannel Message
    EA-->>LK: (relay 控制命令至 R2 Bridge)
    LK-->>R2: DataChannel Message
    R2->>R2: decodeCommand → ROS2 cmd_vel
    R2->>VH: ROS2 /rvep/cmd_vel (linear.x: 0.5, angular.z: 0.3)
    VH-->>R2: ROS2 /odom, /IMU, /Battery
    R2->>R2: encodeTelemetry(odom, imu, battery)
    R2->>LK: DataChannel Publish (Telemetry)
    LK-->>CP: DataChannel Message (Telemetry)
    CP->>CP: decodeTelemetry → TelemetryHUD
    CP-->>O: 更新 HUD (速度、電量、GPS)

    Note over O,VH: 階段 5 — 心跳安全機制 (持續)
    loop 每秒
        CP->>LK: DataChannel Publish (heartbeat)
        LK-->>EA: Heartbeat Received
        EA->>EA: 重置 3 秒超時計時器
    end

    Note over O,VH: 階段 6 — 異常場景：心跳超時
    CP-xLK: 心跳中斷（網路不穩）
    EA->>EA: 3 秒超時 → 進入 Safe Mode
    EA->>GP: IPC: stop (reason: safe_mode)
    GP->>LK: 停止 Video Track
    EA->>LK: DataChannel Publish (SafetyEvent: safe_mode_entered)
    LK-->>CP: SafetyEvent Received
    CP-->>O: SafetyBanner 顯示 + 禁用 Joystick
    O->>CP: 確認安全狀態 → 點擊「恢復控制」
    CP->>LK: DataChannel Publish (resume_control with acknowledgement)
    LK-->>EA: ResumeControlCommand
    EA->>EA: 離開 Safe Mode
    EA->>GP: IPC: start (恢復串流)
    EA->>LK: DataChannel Publish (SafetyEvent: safe_mode_left)
    LK-->>CP: 恢復正常操作

    Note over O,VH: 階段 7 — 釋放控制
    O->>CP: 離開駕駛艙
    CP->>API: POST /api/v1/vehicles/vehicle-001/control-lease/release
    API->>DB: 更新 Lease Status → RELEASED
    DB-->>API: Done
    API-->>CP: Lease Released
    CP->>LK: 離開 LiveKit Room
    LK-->>EA: 收到 Room 空閒通知
